(Design System: AI DevOps Framework) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Overview) Tj
0 -14 Td
(AI DevOps is a developer-operations framework and OpenCode plugin. Its interface language) Tj
0 -14 Td
(should feel like a reliable engineering console: dark by default, compact, status-led, and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(evidence-oriented. The current implemented UI evidence is the MCP Server Dashboard in) Tj
0 -14 Td
(.opencode/server/mcp-dashboard.ts, which uses GitHub-dark colours, compact cards, system) Tj
0 -14 Td
(fonts, blue focus/highlight states, green primary actions, red destructive actions, and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(4px/8px spacing increments.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Design goals:) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Keep operational state obvious: running, stopped, error, authenticated, last update, and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(command actions should scan quickly.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Preserve developer trust with native system typography, code-friendly contrast, visible) Tj
0 -14 Td
(borders, and restrained motion.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Use compact density for dashboards and sidebars, but keep controls at least 44px high when) Tj
0 -14 Td
(touch use is plausible.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Prefer semantic tokens over one-off values so generated reports, OpenCode UI surfaces, and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(dashboard screens stay consistent.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Colors) Tj
0 -14 Td
(The canonical palette is derived from the dashboard CSS in .opencode/server/mcp-dashboard.ts:) Tj
