0 -14 Td
(- Use c9d1d9 or white text on 0d1117, 161b22, 21262d, 238636, and da3633.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Do not use muted text below 12px; pair 6e7681 only with non-critical metadata.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Blue 58a6ff is an accent, not the primary CTA colour; reserve CTA fill for green 238636) Tj
0 -14 Td
(unless the action is navigation/focus.) Tj
0 -14 Td
