0 -14 Td
(Use native system UI fonts for app and dashboard surfaces:) Tj
0 -14 Td
(font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Scale:) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Display: 32px / 700 / 1.15 for handoff covers and major report titles.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Large heading: 24px / 700 / 1.2 for page-level headings.) Tj
0 -14 Td
