0 -14 Td
(- Body: 14px / 400 / 1.5 for dashboard controls and normal UI copy.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Small: 12px / 400-600 for badges, metadata, helper text, and compact buttons.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Code snippets and command examples may use SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo,) Tj
0 -14 Td
(or monospace, but the primary interface remains system sans.) Tj
0 -14 Td
